title: Re: Woman in ‘I’m a professor!’ viral video becomes the new face of the resistance
text:
Woman in ‘I’m a professor!’ viral video becomes the new face of the resistance Posted at 5:13 pm on February 3, 2017 by Greg P. Share on Facebook Share on Twitter 
An unidentified woman who claimed she was a professor at NYU was caught on camera during Thursday night’s protest of conservative speaker Gavin McInnes having a complete meltdown, going after both the cops and NYU students who were there to support McInnes. 
Check it out (Fast-forward to the 10:15 mark): "I'm a professor!" is the new Trigglypuff https://t.co/ZudYe9DQgp @robbysoave 
— Nick Gillespie (@nickgillespie) February 3, 2017 Trending
